title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Aug 10 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Aug 10 2021
description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 2: Cuomo quits, denies all wrongdoing. What's next for Cuomo? The "Anti-Trump" was a fraud. California's Gavin Newsom faces a recall election. Nineteen Republicans senators sell out and support Biden's $1 trillion infrastructure plan. The long list of current democrat scandals. Fauci calls for "unusual things" to fight covid. Democrats will do anything to knock out DeSantis. YouTube bans Sen Rand Paul's comments.
